name: deepseek-code
description: Complete multi-agent AI system with Persistent Sessions, Token-Efficient Pipeline, Semantic Engine, and Intelligence Package. v2.5 adds persistent multi-session conversations with continuity: system prompt sent once, parent_message_id chaining, parallel named sessions across CLI invocations. v2.4 save_response.py writes DeepSeek output directly to disk via pipe, cutting Claude token usage ~96%. Pure-Python TF-IDF semantic matching, Bayesian inference, temporal decay, Mann-Kendall trend detection. 5 intelligence features. Plus: V3.2 auto-select model, thinking mode, quantum dual sessions, multi-step plans, semantic memory, 51 skills with TF-IDF matching, and 15 MCP tools.
